name: Jordan 13 Retro Atmosphere Grey
description: The Air Jordan 13 'Atmosphere Grey' emerges with a neutral look. The shoe's white leather base is overlaid by quilted tumbled leather in grey, with a lighter grey on the suede panel that runs from the heel to the base of the midfoot. A green hologram logo brings color to the ankle, while the lining and Jumpman branding add contrast in black. Underfoot, the podular Zoom Air midsole gives way to a black panther's paw-inspired outsole.
